
Overview of noun drama

The noun drama has 4 senses (first 4 from tagged texts)
                                          
1. (12) play, drama, dramatic play -- (a dramatic work intended for performance by actors on a stage; "he wrote several plays but only one was produced on Broadway")
2. (7) drama, dramatic event -- (an episode that is turbulent or highly emotional)
3. (2) drama -- (the literary genre of works intended for the theater)
4. (1) drama -- (the quality of being arresting or highly emotional)
